title: Test Eleventy Site
description: This is a test site using Eleventy (11ty.io), a static site generator written in JavaScript. It is intended to be a boilerplate for future 11ty projects
author: Zac Heisey

staticgen.description: A simpler static site generator. An alternative to Jekyll. Written in JavaScript. Transforms a directory of templates (of varying types) into HTML. Works with HTML, Markdown, Liquid, Nunjucks, Handlebars, Mustache, EJS, Haml, Pug, and JavaScript Template Literals.
